title: Volkswagen Driver - April 2016
description:
English | 92 pages | PDF | 37.7 MB

Volkswagen Driver is probably the world's most authoritative English-language magazine which deals with the Volkswagen brand. Our team of writers has outstanding knowledge, covering the whole period from the development of the original Beetle to the most up-to-date models. We publish independent, fully-detailed road test reports of all the latest models, historical features, articles about owner and their cars, features about VW motor caravan and light commercials, and cover all aspects of Volkswagen motorsport, tuning and modification
